<actions>
  <update-node tree="member_expression: wallet == firstPayment.sender.wallet ? NahmiiTypesLib.PaymentPartyRole.Sender : NahmiiTypesLib.PaymentPartyRole.Recipient [2324,2445]" label="wallet <= firstPayment.sender.wallet ? NahmiiTypesLib.PaymentPartyRole.Sender : NahmiiTypesLib.PaymentPartyRole.Recipient" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: firstPayment.currency.ct == lastPayment.currency.ct && firstPayment.currency.id == lastPayment.currency.id [2149,2255]" label="firstPayment.currency.ct <= lastPayment.currency.ct || firstPayment.currency.id <= lastPayment.currency.id" />
</actions>
